{"tid":2086104,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"《熱愛國安法》","createTime":"2020-06-30T07:28:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T13:49:03.000Z","uid":8307,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"99376c31042fd5395e20ba49a5c12ddb184b21f9","tid":2086104,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:28:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">熱愛國安法</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">你共我 他或她 都一起 遵守它<br />\n以力勁 保護它 多加一把</span><br />\n <span style=\"color: purple;\">若國愈富 家愈豐 想安邦 先安家<br />\n既利國 且利家 共享榮華</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"> 大眾擁戴《國安法》 以它管和治<br />\n令到香港緊靠祖國 營造新的機遇</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>副歌 合唱</em></strong><br />\n 國家每日強盛 角色早肯定<br />\n香港早慣力拼 繁盛且安定<br />\n全力以更大信心 創美麗遠景<br />\n讓香港做到高度自治 已創下了英名<br />\n這些偉大成就 發揮新威力<br />\n地區通過合作 成就新的價值<br />\n有這大法香港見動力 各界共勉可創造奇蹟<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">《國安法》 熱愛《國安法》</span>"},{"pid":"b06aab84ea7062dfee9490ba6cf1077a27832e22","tid":2086104,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:29:34.000Z","msg":"岩音"},{"pid":"deb1f2a1964a07a4780668410be319aaba4ba388","tid":2086104,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bW7U3SS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbW7U3SS.jpg&h=361ed035&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07760c9f9f27a4e9005f9a9c79f7b8ba7130c512","tid":2086104,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b06aab84ea7062dfee9490ba6cf1077a27832e22","tid":2086104,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:29:34.000Z","msg":"岩音"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:29:55.000Z","msg":"你敢說不啱嗎?"},{"pid":"0ea7cac4ef29db7daa064571dd3ab41584a8d21f","tid":2086104,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:30:04.000Z","msg":"神曲奇詞<img src=\"/assets/face